==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Herbal
<hw>Herb"al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A book
containing the names and descriptions of plants.</def>
<rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A collection of specimens of plants, dried and
preserved; a hortus siccus; an herbarium.</def>
<rj><au>Steele.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Herbalism</ent>⟦br⟧
